      <title>查尔斯国王最近住院后正在接受癌症治疗</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/king-charles-iii-diagnosed-with-cancer-buckingham-palace-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白金汉宫表示，国王查理三世已被诊断出患有癌症，这位75岁的君主现在将接受治疗，在此期间他将无法履行公共职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/king-charles-iii-diagnosed-with-cancer-buckingham-palace-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 18:08:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林德纳表示，德国极右翼选择党对经济构成风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/germany-s-far-right-afd-is-a-risk-for-economy-lindner-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳表示，德国极右翼选择党对经济构成风险，因为它可能会阻碍国际企业的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/germany-s-far-right-afd-is-a-risk-for-economy-lindner-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:46:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲对清洁技术保护主义对绿色转型成本的影响保持警惕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/europe-wary-of-clean-tech-protectionism-on-green-transition-cost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟正在回避采取进一步措施来保护陷入困境的清洁技术产业免受中国廉价进口产品的影响，因为担心这可能会加大关键零部件的采购难度并提高绿色转型的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/europe-wary-of-clean-tech-protectionism-on-green-transition-cost</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>海利·坎普 (Haley Camp) 拒绝批评 2024 年申办依赖于民主党选民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/haley-camp-rejects-critique-2024-bid-relies-on-democratic-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼基·哈利 (Nikki Haley) 的竞选经理表示，随着这位前联合国大使开始竞选共和党总统提名，他们正在争取独立选民，尽管有人批评这位候选人依赖民主党和左倾个人来推动她的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/haley-camp-rejects-critique-2024-bid-relies-on-democratic-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 17:23:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>10 月 7 日指控后，联合国对近东救济工程处“中立性”展开调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/un-opens-probe-of-unrwa-neutrality-after-oct-7-allegations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在捐助国对部分工作人员参与 10 月 7 日针对以色列的袭击的指控感到畏惧后，联合国正在对其巴勒斯坦援助机构进行外部审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/un-opens-probe-of-unrwa-neutrality-after-oct-7-allegations</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 16:56:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
